            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-bold text-emerald-600 tnum">5</span><span>Go to <strong>Tools &rarr; Import &rarr; NinjaScript Add-On</strong> and select the new <code class="text-[13px] bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">.zip</code>.</span></li>
