            <strong class="text-zinc-900">Your settings carry over automatically.</strong> Updating never resets
            your license, trading profile, Guard rules, journal, or session history. If you ever import
            <em>without</em> removing the old version first and NinjaTrader shows a compile error, just do the
            Remove step above and import again.
