              <li class="flex gap-2.5"><span class="font-bold text-emerald-600 tnum">1</span><span>Make sure your SIM or live account is connected in NinjaTrader</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2.5"><span class="font-bold text-emerald-600 tnum">2</span><span>Click <strong>Refresh accounts</strong> in Meridian</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-2.5"><span class="font-bold text-emerald-600 tnum">3</span><span>If needed, close and reopen the Meridian Dashboard</span></li>
            </ol>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">If the issue continues, send a screenshot to support.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-[#fafafa] p-7">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">PSI shows Warning or Critical on the first SIM trade</h3>
